OL,3,CManchester City's hearing into alleged
OL,4,Cfinancial breaches to get under way
OL,6,FManchester City's long-awaited hearing
OL,7,Finto alleged breaches of the Premier
OL,8,FLeague's financial regulations is set
OL,9,Fto begin on Monday, 16 September.
OL,11,FThe champions are facing 115 charges
OL,12,Fof breaking the competition's rules
OL,13,Fdating back to the 2009-10 season.
OL,15,FIt is thought the club, who are also
OL,16,Faccused of failing to co-operate with
OL,17,Fan investigation, could face a range
OL,18,Fof punishments including a severe
OL,19,Fpoints penalty or even expulsion from
OL,20,Fthe Premier League if found guilty.
