OL,3,CManchester City's hearing into alleged
OL,4,Cfinancial breaches to get under way
OL,6,FThe case will be heard by an
OL,7,Findependent commission at an
OL,8,Fundisclosed location and could take 10
OL,9,Fweeks to complete, with a verdict not
OL,10,Fannounced until 2025.
OL,12,FCity were charged by the league in
OL,13,FFebruary 2023 after a long
OL,14,Finvestigation into allegations
OL,15,Fpublished by German magazine Der
OL,16,FSpiegel in autumn 2018.
OL,18,FThe club deny any wrongdoing and have
OL,19,Fpreviously said they have a
OL,20,F"comprehensive body of irrefutable
OL,21,Fevidence" to support their stance.
