OL,3,CManchester City's hearing into alleged
OL,4,Cfinancial breaches to get under way
OL,6,FCity's financial affairs have come
OL,7,Funder regular scrutiny since their
OL,8,Ftakeover by Sheikh Mansour's Abu Dhabi
OL,9,FUnited Group in 2008.
OL,11,FIn 2020 they were banned from European
OL,12,Fcompetition after being found guilty
OL,13,Fof breaking UEFA's Financial Fair Play
OL,14,Frules, but successfully challenged
OL,15,Fthat ruling at the Court of
OL,16,FArbitration for Sport.
